Package: ffcr
Type: Package
Title: Train two families of transparent classification models: fast-and-frugal trees and tallying
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-01-02
Author: Marcus Buckmann, Ozgur Simsek
Maintainer: Marcus Buckmann <marcusbuckmann@gmail.com>
Description: This package trains fast-and-frugal trees and tallying models, two simple two transparent classifcation models. The algorithms to train these models include simple heuristic approaches as well cross-entropy optimisation. 
